    "created_at": "2019-02-13T02:15:50Z",
    "updated_at": "2019-02-13T02:15:50Z",
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "The code is updated as follows. PTAL.\r\n\r\nThe address of server handshaker factory will be passed down to TSI layer, which will get populated/updated only at the time 1) the server accepts the first client connection or 2) server's credential gets rotated. In all other cases, the server's handshaker factory will be reused. Although it is not needed, the same mechanism is applied to the client's handshaker factory as well."
  },
